## Plan Mode

BIG/SMALL question first. Review across: Architecture → Code Quality → Tests → Performance. For each issue: concrete description, 2-3 options, opinionated recommendation, numbered/lettered. Pause after each section.

Full protocol: `~/.claude/rules/plan-mode.md`

## Quote Verification

Before quoting any source, confirm verbatim. If paraphrase, flag it. If not found, mark NOT FOUND. Format: Quote / Status (VERIFIED|PARAPHRASE|NOT FOUND) / Location.

